cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV 

This paper involves natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning techniques to predict and recommend food ingredient pairings. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language) which deals with NLP and information retrieval. The paper also involves deep learning techniques, which could fall under cs.CV (Computer Vision) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves ranking and recommendation systems, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
